AB^2 + BC^2 &= AC^2 \\
90^2 + x^2 &= (2x - 6)^2 \\
8100 + x^2 &= 4x^2 - 24x + 36 \\
0 &= 3x^2 - 24x - 8064 \\
0 &= x^2 - 8x - 2688 \\
